<droneBlueprint name="CO_BALLISTATOG_DEFEND">
	<type>BATTLE</type>
	<locked>1</locked>
	<tip>tip_toggle_crew</tip>
	<title>Ballista Drone [Anti-Pers]</title>
	<short>Ballista [DEF]</short>
	<desc>[CURRENT MODE: Anti-Personnel] Manually controlled personnel drone that can be toggled to act as either a Defensive Anti-Personnel or Boarding drone.
Whoever was the genius who decided to get the ballista onto a spaceship, encase it in armor, is probably really a genius for not giving this Greek-era wonder an AI.

-100 HP, 0.9x combat damage taken, 10x combat damage, can't sabotage
-0.7x movement speed, requires a friendly crew to be in the same room to move around
-Requires a friendly crew to be in the same room to be able to shoot. While in the same room as the ballista, friendly crew loses the ability to fight or sabotage.
-Operators don't lose the ability to fight or sabotage</desc>
	<power>2</power>
	<cost>70</cost>
	<rarity>2</rarity>
	<iconImage>battle</iconImage>
</droneBlueprint>
<droneBlueprint name="CO_BALLISTATOG_BOARDER">
	<type>BOARDER</type>
	<tip>tip_toggle_crew</tip>
	<locked>1</locked>
	<title>Ballista Drone [Boarding]</title>
	<short>Ballista [ATK]</short>
	<desc>[CURRENT MODE: Boarding] Manually controlled personnel drone that can be toggled to act as either a Defensive Anti-Personnel or Boarding drone.
Whoever was the genius who decided to get the ballista onto a spaceship, encase it in armor, is probably really a genius for not giving this Greek-era wonder an AI.

-100 HP, 0.9x combat damage taken, 10x combat damage, can't sabotage
-0.7x movement speed, requires a friendly crew to be in the same room to move around
-Requires a friendly crew to be in the same room to be able to shoot. While in the same room as the ballista, friendly crew loses the ability to fight or sabotage.
-Operators don't lose the ability to fight or sabotage</desc>
	<power>2</power>
	<speed>18</speed>
	<cost>70</cost>
	<rarity>0</rarity>
	<iconImage>boarder</iconImage>
</droneBlueprint>


<droneBlueprint name="CO_COMMITTOG_DEFEND">
	<type>BATTLE</type>
	<locked>1</locked>
	<tip>tip_toggle_crew</tip>
	<title>Commit Drone [Anti-Pers]</title>
	<short>Commit [DEF]</short>
	<desc>[CURRENT MODE: Anti-Personnel] Manually controlled personnel drone that can be toggled to act as either a Defensive Anti-Personnel or Boarding drone.
A special model of ballista drone invented by the Legion. With the use of aether technologies and larger bolts, the ballista's combat effectiveness has been significantly increased.

-130 HP, 0.7x combat damage taken, 20x combat damage, can't sabotage
-0.5x movement speed, doesn't require a friendly crew to be in the same room to move around
-Requires a friendly crew to be in the same room to be able to shoot. While in the same room as the ballista, friendly crew loses the ability to fight or sabotage.
-Operators don't lose the ability to fight or sabotage</desc>
	<power>3</power>
	<cost>110</cost>
	<rarity>0</rarity>
	<iconImage>battle</iconImage>
</droneBlueprint>
