<crewBlueprint name="co_human_legion_oper">
	<desc>Trained in Universe 1 and hand-picked from the finest of the MFK ranks, the Legionnaires are the deadliest Rebels you'll ever meet.
	
	Inherited Human stat: minor suffocation resistance</desc>
	<cost>195</cost>
	<title>Legionnaire Operator</title>
	<short>Operator</short>
	<rarity>0</rarity>
	<powerList>
		<power>Active Ability: Summons a temporary Commit drone ally which moves slowly, but can only fight if there is an allied crew in the same room.</power>
		<power>Passively heals nearby allied drones for 2hp/s</power>
		<power>Passively heals itself for 1.5hp/s when below 55hp</power>
		<power>Inflicts 2.2x damage in crew combat, 0.8x combat damage taken</power>
		<power>Repair speed is quadrupled, extinguishes fires five times faster</power>
		<power>Greatly resistant to O2 and fire hazards</power>
		<power>Trained in lvl2 skills, cannot be cloned</power>
		<power>Carries a short range personal teleporter that allows it to teleport anywhere on the current ship
		</power>
		<power>You better not know what happens if it dies</power>
	</powerList>
</crewBlueprint>



