<crewBlueprint name="co_ravager_fatum_aurora">
	<desc>"The Ravagers.. It's like I'm conducting their music. Every move, every order is executed impreccably. We are one. One... But we need resources. The power such as ours requires all the #4|7!verse can offer!"

This robotic spider, completely subservient to the Ravager Mind, can be a serious obstacle on the battlefield. If it's not on your side, it's best to prevent them from gathering.
Equipped with the Laser Minigun 'Aurora'.</desc>
	<cost>110</cost>
	<title>Ravager, M1FT1A</title>
	<short>'Fatum' [A]</short>
	<rarity>0</rarity>
	<powerList>
		<power>125 HP, 0.9x all damage taken, 1.1x fire damage taken, immune to suffocation and mind control</power>
		<power>1.5x movement speed, 0.1x combat damage, 0.2x sabotage speed, 10x shooting speed</power>
		<power>Debuffs targeted crew, causing them to take more damage with each hit, up to 3x the original damage</power>
		<power>Cannot heal from most sources or be cloned, regenerates 4.5hp/s if unharmed for 10 seconds</power>
	</powerList>
</crewBlueprint>
