		<power>125 HP, 0.9x all damage taken, 1.1x fire damage taken, immune to suffocation and mind control</power>
		<power>1.5x movement speed, 0.1x combat damage, 0.05x sabotage speed, 10x shooting speed</power>
		<power>In addition to attacking the main target, it deals minor continuous damage to all enemies in the room</power>
		<power>Debuffs targeted crew, continuously decreasing their movement speed and combat damage to 0.3x of their original values, as well as disables their active abilities</power>
		<power>Cannot heal from most sources or be cloned, regenerates 4.5hp/s if unharmed for 10 seconds</power>
	</powerList>
</crewBlueprint>


