	<desc>UOY T'NDLUOHD EES SHIT</desc>  <!-- ~40% crossout desc-->
	<descriptionOverride>Not so hich-tech weapon developed by the Ravagers, however ideal for high-tonnage ships. Incredibly accurate and reliable, capable of dealing colossal damage when fully charged and kept on target.

		Stats:
		Required Power: 6
		Charge Time: 18 seconds
		Accuracy Bonus: +35%
		
		Shots Per Charge: 12
		
		Base Hull Damage: 1
		Total Crew Damage: 10
		Shield Piercing: 2
		
		Breach Chance: 20%

		Perk: If all projectiles in a single burst hit the hull, every third projectile in the next burst gets 1 additional hull, system and crew damage. Firing with the perk active doesn't charge the perk.
		
		Default Price: 160~   -   Selling Price: 80~
	</descriptionOverride>
	<tooltip>If all projectiles in a single burst hit the hull, every third projectile in the next burst gets 1 additional hull, system and crew damage. Firing with the perk active doesn't charge the perk.</tooltip>
