<augBlueprint name="CO_RAVAGER_SYSOPER">
	<title>Ravager's Operating System</title>
	<desc>The "mind" of this machine can control systems at level 1 and detect life forms even with sensors disabled.</desc>
	<cost>0</cost>
	<rarity>0</rarity>
	<stackable>false</stackable>
	<locked>true</locked>
</augBlueprint>

<augBlueprint name="CO_RAVAGER_PLATING">
	<title>Ravager Plating</title>
	<desc>This hull plating automatically patches breaches and put out fires very fast, also absorbs 10% of scrap into the hull, repairing it. It will not take scrap when your hull is at full capacity.
Ravagers became memorable not so much for their endurance, but for their ability to assimilate.</desc>
	<cost>0</cost>
	<rarity>0</rarity>
	<stackable>false</stackable>
	<locked>true</locked>
</augBlueprint>

<augBlueprint name="CO_RAVAGER_PROTOCOL">
	<title>Devastating Protocols</title>
	<desc>"They're just machines... soulless, cruel, without any feelings or desires, just machines. Aren't they?"
All enemy crew become susceptible to suffocation, while all onboard drones are devoured by the ship's hull, offering no resistance.</desc>
	<cost>0</cost>
	<rarity>0</rarity>
	<stackable>false</stackable>
	<locked>true</locked>
</augBlueprint>

<augBlueprint name="CO_RAVAGER_ENERSHIELD">
	<title>Ravager Shielding</title>
	<desc>Energy Shield technology improved by Ravagers. It has 36 hit points, replaces shields generated by the shield system.
This Energy Shield regenerates over time while the shield system is active. Enemy crew can no longer return to their ship if they teleport to a ship with this shielding installed.</desc>
	<cost>0</cost>
	<rarity>0</rarity>
	<stackable>false</stackable>
	<locked>true</locked>
</augBlueprint>

<augBlueprint name="CO_RAVAGER_FADING_CLOAK">
	<title>Fading Cloaking</title>
	<desc>Legends say that the Fading Ravagers were those who renounced the ideas of their own artificial mind, thus separating themselves from the Foothold. Such "separatists" suffered a fate worse than their usual prey had ever experienced.
When installed, shortens Cloaking cooldown by 15 second.</desc>
	<cost>0</cost>
	<rarity>0</rarity>
	<value>3</value>
